UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc6='Your next choice awaits.$B$BYou are on a diplomatic mission for your liege to a cruel country that is currently at war with yours.  The war has been costly on both sides.  Your mission is to secure a peace that is honorable to both peoples.$B$BAt a diplomatic dinner, you overhear the ruler of the opposing land viciously insult your benevolent liege.  You are fairly certain the ruler meant to say it out of your earshot, but nonetheless he has besmirched your liege\'s honor.$B$BMake your choice.$B$B$B' WHERE entry=7361; /* Text0_0: Your next choice awaits.$B$BYou are on a diplomatic mission for your liege to a cruel country that is currently at war with yours.  The war has been costly on both sides.  Your mission is to secure a peace that is honorable to both peoples.$B$BAt a diplomatic dinner, you overhear the ruler of the opposing land viciously insult your benevolent liege.  You are fairly certain the ruler meant to say it out of your earshot, but nonetheless he has besmirched your liege\'s honor.$B$BMake your choice.$B$B$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc6='Your next choice awaits.$B$BYour brother seeks to join the ranks of the prestigious military order you are already a part of.  While you are sure of his commitment and loyalty, his talent and ability to perform the arduous tasks of the order is what you question.  While you are not certain he will be able to rise to the challenge of the order - putting you and others in danger - you are certain that your word alone would allow him in or keep him out.$B$BMake your choice.$B$B' WHERE entry=7362; /* Text0_0: Your next choice awaits.$B$BYour brother seeks to join the ranks of the prestigious military order you are already a part of.  While you are sure of his commitment and loyalty, his talent and ability to perform the arduous tasks of the order is what you question.  While you are not certain he will be able to rise to the challenge of the order - putting you and others in danger - you are certain that your word alone would allow him in or keep him out.$B$BMake your choice.$B$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc6='Your next choice awaits.$B$BYou alone have defeated a terrible beast that has been ravaging the countryside, taking its ear as a trophy.  You later learn that your liege had offered a reward for the beast\'s death, and that a kind but destitute knight who you know is trying to support a family by meager means claims the beast\'s kill as his own.  You have no real need for money yourself, but you know that the destitute knight is lying for his own personal gain.$B$BMake your choice.$B$B' WHERE entry=7363; /* Text0_0: Your next choice awaits.$B$BYou alone have defeated a terrible beast that has been ravaging the countryside, taking its ear as a trophy.  You later learn that your liege had offered a reward for the beast\'s death, and that a kind but destitute knight who you know is trying to support a family by meager means claims the beast\'s kill as his own.  You have no real need for money yourself, but you know that the destitute knight is lying for his own personal gain.$B$BMake your choice.$B$B */
