UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc6='Mortals, I am indebted to you for freeing me from the terrible corruption that besets this place. Though I have not yet recovered fully, I can help you battle Yogg-Saron.$B$BI can grant you and your friends the Speed of Invention, increasing your damage and movement speed. In addition, I can destabilize the matrices of certain Saronite based life-forms, reducing their attack and casting speeds.' WHERE entry=14334; /* Text0_0: Mortals, I am indebted to you for freeing me from the terrible corruption that besets this place. Though I have not yet recovered fully, I can help you battle Yogg-Saron.$B$BI can grant you and your friends the Speed of Invention, increasing your damage and movement speed. In addition, I can destabilize the matrices of certain Saronite based life-forms, reducing their attack and casting speeds. */
